snippet.title: SpongeBob's Truth or Square PSP Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
SpongeBob's Truth or Square PSP Gameplay HD.

SpongeBob's Truth or Square is a video game based on the SpongeBob SquarePants episode with the same title. It was released on October 26, 2009. This video game is based on SpongeBob's 10th anniversary. It is the first SpongeBob game since SpongeBob SquarePants: The Yellow Avenger to be released on the PlayStation Portable. This is also the third SpongeBob game developed by Heavy Iron Studios. It can be considered a sequel to Battle for Bikini Bottom, as it is developed by the same company and has recycled sound effects and music.
